title: JR Terrier and the Big Break
description: Guess who's going to Hollywood? JR Terrier in this new series called JR Terrier and the Big Break. Jr becomes famous, but will all that fame go to his head? Will he leave his friends behind for the glamorous lifestyle? What will he do. See JR made the biggest decision of his life. Either way, it will be big!
author: Tiffany Brianne
